    'context' => 'design/standard/setup/init',
    'source' => 'If you don\'t have access to a database, you should obtain access now. eZ Publish is capable of running multiple sites, each site needs its own database. This means that you need to create several databases if you plan to run multiple sites. Please refer to the database system user manual if you\'re unsure about how to create a database.',
